description:
&lt;p&gt;Frimley Health NHS Foundation Trust is looking for a full-time, non-invasive Consultant Cardiologist to cover Maternity leave. The locum will be based on the Wexham Park Hospital site for a fixed term period of six months to start as soon as possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will join a team of 11 Cardiologists, with a variety of sub-speciality interests, working in a busy general Cardiology Department and be expected to provide care on the Coronary Care Unit, Acute Cardiology ward and in Cardiology Outpatient Department. There is a 1:8 commitment to an inpatient ‘Consultant of the week’ rota during which time other duties will be reduced.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDr Peter ClarksonAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details/informal visits please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Peter Clarkson, Cardiology Lead on 01753-633000 or peter.clarkson@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Gareth Roberts, Chief of Service, General Medicine &amp; Emergency Services on 01753-633000 or gareth.roberts2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
